text: Tian Zhandong (born 13 April 1983) is a Chinese ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of China Category:Ski jumpers at the 2011 Asian Winter Games Category:Ski jumpers at the 2017 Asian Winter Games Category:People from Tonghua
